<p></p><div class="quoteright" style="width:281px;"><div class="lazy_load_img_box" style="padding-top:164.41%"><img src="https://static.tvtropes.org/pmwiki/pub/images/51ru2fzvnql_sx326_bo1204203200.jpg" class="embeddedimage" border="0" alt="https://static.tvtropes.org/pmwiki/pub/images/51ru2fzvnql_sx326_bo1204203200.jpg" width="281" height="462"></div></div>An <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/Anthology" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/Anthology">Anthology</a> series, featuring multiple authors who were specially asked to write for the <em><a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Franchise/Batman" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Franchise/Batman">Batman</a></em> multimedia franchise. <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/MartinHGreenberg" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/MartinHGreenberg">Martin H. Greenberg</a> acted as acquiring editor. The books are published by <a class="createlink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/BantamBooks" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/BantamBooks">Bantam Books</a>, and several of the short stories were reprinted in another of Greenberg's anthologies, <em><a class="createlink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Literature/TalesOfTheBatman" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Literature/TalesOfTheBatman">Tales Of The Batman</a></em>.<hr><h2>Anthology titles:</h2><div class="proper-ad-unit mobile-ad square_ad"><h6 class="ad-caption">Advertisement:</h6><div id="proper-ad-tvtropes_mobile_ad_1"><script>propertag.cmd.push(function() { proper_display('tvtropes_mobile_ad_1'); })</script></div></div><ul><li> <em>The Further Adventures of Batman</em> (1989)</li><li> <em>The Further Adventures of The Joker</em> (1990)</li><li> <em>The Further Adventures of Batman Volume 2: Featuring the Penguin</em> (1992)</li><li> <em>The Further Adventures of Batman Volume 3: Featuring Catwoman</em> (1993)</li></ul><hr><h2>Works in the anthologies:</h2><div class="folderlabel" onclick="togglefolder('folder0');">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<em>The Further Adventures of Batman</em>&nbsp;</div><div id="folder0" class="folder" isfolder="true" style="display:block;"><ul><li> "<a class="createlink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Literature/DeathOfTheDreammaster" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Literature/DeathOfTheDreammaster">Death Of The Dreammaster</a>"; by <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/RobertSheckley" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/RobertSheckley">Robert Sheckley</a></li><li> "<a class="createlink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Literature/Bats" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Literature/Bats">Bats</a>"; by <a class="createlink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/HenrySlesar" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/HenrySlesar">Henry Slesar</a></li><li> "<a class="createlink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Literature/SubwayJack" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Literature/SubwayJack">Subway Jack</a>"; by <a class="createlink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/JoeRLansdale" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/JoeRLansdale">Joe R Lansdale</a></li><li> "<a class="createlink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Literature/TheSoundOfOneHandClapping" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Literature/TheSoundOfOneHandClapping">The Sound Of One Hand Clapping</a>"; by <a class="createlink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/MaxAllenCollins" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/MaxAllenCollins">Max Allen Collins</a></li><li> "<a class="createlink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Literature/NeutralGround" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Literature/NeutralGround">Neutral Ground</a>"; by <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/MikeResnick" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/MikeResnick">Mike Resnick</a></li><li> "<a class="createlink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Literature/BatmanInNighttown" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Literature/BatmanInNighttown">Batman In Nighttown</a>"; by <a class="createlink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/KarenHaber" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/KarenHaber">Karen Haber</a> and <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/RobertSilverberg" title